y Central]]''\n*''[[The Comic Strip (TV series)|The Comic Strip]]''\n*''[[Count Duckula]]''\n*''[[Courage the Cowardly Dog]]''\n*''[[Cow and Chicken]]''\n*''[[Cybernet]]''\n*''[[C.B. Bears]]''\n*''[[COPS (animated TV series)|C.O.P.S.]]''\n*''[[Degrassi Junior High]]''\n*''[[Dennis the Menace (1986 TV series)|Dennis the Menace]]''\n*''[[Denver, the Last Dinosaur]]''\n*''[[Detention (TV series)|Detention]]''\n*''[[Dexter's Laboratory]]''\n*''[[Dink, the Little Dinosaur]]''\n*''[[Dinosaurs (TV series)|Dinosaurs]]''\n*''[[Diplodos]]''\n*''[[Zukkoke Knight - Don De La Mancha|Don Quixote]]''\n*''[[Don't Blame the Koalas]]''\n*''[[Dragon Tales]]''\n*''[[Droopy, Master Detective]]''\n*''[[The Dukes (TV series)|The Dukes]]''\n*''[[Eckhart (TV series)|Eckhart]]''\n*''[[Ed, Edd n' Eddy]]''\n*''[[Eekstravaganza]]''\n*''[[Eek! the Cat]]''\n*''[[Explorations (TV series)|Explorations]]''\n*''[[Fangface]]''\n*''[[Fantastic Max]]''\n*''[[Fat Albert and the Cosby Kids]]''\n*''[[Fish Police]]''\n*''[[The Flintstones]]''\n*''[[Flipper and Lopaka]]''\n*''[[For Better or For Worse]]''\n*''[[Fox's Peter Pan and the Pirates]]''\n*''[[Frankenstein Jr. and the Impossibles]]''\n*''[[Freakazoid!]]''\n*''[[The Fresh Prince of Bel-Air]]''\n*''The Fun Club''\n*''[[The Funky Phantom]]''\n*''[[The Further Adventures of SuperTed]]''\n*''[[Gadget and the Gadgetinis]]''\n*''[[Galaxy Goof-Ups]]''\n*''[[Garfield and Friends]]''\n*''[[Get Smart]]''\n*''[[The Gift (Australian children's TV series)|The Gift]]''\n*''[[Gilligan's Island]]''\n*''Gloria's House''\n*''[[Going Bananas (U.S. series)|Going Bananas]]''\n*''[[Good Times]]''\n*''[[Grown Ups (1999 TV series)|Grown Ups]]''\n*''[[Saban\u2019s Gulliver\u2019s Travels|Gulliver's Travels]]''\n*''[[Hammerman]]''\n*''[[Hang Time (TV series)|Hang Time]]''\n*''[[Happily Ever After: Fairy Tales for Every Child]]''\n*''[[Heathcliff (1980 TV series)|The Heathcliff and Dingbat Show]]''\n*''[[Heathcliff (1984 TV series)|Heathcliff & the Catillac Cats]]''\n*''[[Help