-View_6_JPEG_FT.jpg Radisson Blu Capital]\n|[[Nicosia]]\n|150m\n|492ft\n|33\n|\n|Proposed\n|Hotel / Residential\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.papachristou.org/project/radisson-blu-capital/|title=Radisson Blu Capital|website=Eraclis Papachristou|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-21}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#FFB347;\"\n|6\n|[https://trilogylimassol.com/storage/app/media/homepage/2.Towers-home-page1670x1150.jpg '''Trilogy'''] <small>North Tower (2/3)</small>\n|[[Limassol]]\n| 148m\n|486ft\n| 37\n|2023\n|Broke Ground\n|Residential\n|<small>Piling of Trilogy's North Tower has been completed<ref name=\":0\" /></small>\n|- style=\"background:#FFB347;\"\n|7\n|[https://trilogylimassol.com/storage/app/media/homepage/2.Towers-home-page1670x1150.jpg '''Trilogy'''] <small>East Tower (3/3)</small>\n|[[Limassol]]\n| 148m\n|486ft\n| 36\n|2022\n|Under Construction\n|Mixed Use\n|<small>Concrete foundations poured. Now climbing above ground level<ref name=\":0\" /></small>\n|- style=\"background:#FFB347;\"\n|8\n|[http://cyfield360.com/uploads/images/ik1c6.jpg '''360 Nicosia''']\n|[[Nicosia]]\n|135m\n|443ft\n|34\n|2020\n|Under Construction\n|Mixed Use\n|<small>[[Nicosia]]</small><small>'s tallest building. Almost completed<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://cyfield360.com/|title=Cyfield 360|website=cyfield360.com|access-date=2020-01-28}}</ref></small>\n|-\n|-\n|-\n|- style=\"background:#FFB347;\"\n|9\n|'''[https://limassolblumarine.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/banner-2-1.jpg Blu Marine]''' <small>'''Poseidon''' (1/2)</small>\n|[[Limassol]]\n|\u2248130m\n|\u2248426,5ft\n|33\n|2022\n|Under Construction\n|Mixed Use\n|<small>Groundworks stage<ref name=\":3\">{{Cite web|url=https://limassolblumarine.com/|title=Limassol Blu Marine {{!}} Home|website=Limassol Blu Marine|language=en-US|access-date=2020-01-28}}</ref></small>\n|- style=\"background:#FFB347;\"\n|10\n|'''[https://www.pafilia.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/neo-hero-1920x900.jpg Limassol NEO]''' <small>'''Kaia''' (2/4)</small>\n