us]]</small><small>' first integrated casino resort, the only one of its kind in Europe. Concrete foundations poured. Now climbing above ground level<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cityofdreamsmed.com.cy/en/home.html|title=City of Dreams Mediterranean|website=www.cityofdreamsmed.com.cy|access-date=2020-01-28}}</ref></small>\n|-\n|- style=\"background: pink;\"\n|44\n|[https://archello.s3.eu-central-1.amazonaws.com/images/2019/08/01/eraclispapachristou-limassol--1-.1564672826.0237.jpg '''C High-rise''']\n|[[Limassol]]\n|\u224875m\n|\u2248246ft\n|19\n|\n|Proposed\n|Residential\n|<small><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://archello.com/project/c-high-rise|title=C High-Rise {{!}} Eraclis Papachristou Architects|website=Archello|language=en|access-date=2020-01-28}}</ref></small>\n|- style=\"background: pink;\"\n|45\n|[https://www.armeftis.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/architects-cyprus-1024x683.jpg '''Mandarin Park''']\n|[[Limassol]]\n|71,7m\n|235ft\n|16\n|2024\n|Proposed\n|Residential\n|<small>A residential tower to be erected at [[Limassol]]'s tourist area after the demolishion of an older building<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://in-cyprus.com/mandarin-park-a-16-storey-tower-in-germasoyia/|title=\u201cMandarin Park\u201d: A 16-storey tower in Germasoyia|last=|first=|date=|website=In-Cyprus.com|language=en-US|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-01-30}}</ref></small>\n|- style=\"background:#87CEFA;\"\n|46\n|[http://www.philenews.com/temp/images/1050x3000/cache_1050x3000_Analog_medium_687718_163055_1642019.JPG '''Soho Resort'''] <small>(1/2)</small>\n|[[Paphos]]\n|71m\n|233ft\n|16\n|2022\n|Approved\n|Residential\n|<small>No works have began as of yet<ref name=\":6\" /></small>\n|-\n|- style=\"background: pink;\"\n|47\n|[http://www.philenews.com/temp/images/728x3000/cache_728x3000_Analog_medium_738712_4157670_1072019.JPG '''Radisson Residences''']\n|[[Larnaca]]\n|69m\n|226ft\n|19\n|\n|Proposed\n|Mixed Use\n|<small><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.qualitydevelopmen